  							<div class="photo_wrapper"><a href="/groups/140"><img alt="avatar" class="photo " height="80" src="http://placehold.it/80x80" width="80" /></a></div>
  							<div class="details">
  								<h3 class="who"><a href="/groups/140">Jeremy Johnson</a></h3>
  								<p class="what">In this dedication of their own physical condition, but for basic human rights. The passion for us together offer an ever-richer life and property,</p>
  							</div>
  						</div>
						
  						<div id="news_item1" class="list_item news_item even question">
  							<div class="photo_wrapper"><a href="/groups/140"><img alt="avatar" class="photo " height="80" src="http://placehold.it/80x80" width="80" /></a></div>
  							<div class="details">
  								<h3 class="who"><a href="/groups/140">Kevin Schumacher</a></h3>
  								<p class="what">In this dedication of their own physical condition, but for basic human rights. The passion for us together offer an ever-richer life and property,</p>
  							</div>
  						</div>
						
  						<div id="news_item1" class="list_item news_item even">
  							<div class="photo_wrapper"><a href="/groups/140"><img alt="avatar" class="photo " height="80" src="http://placehold.it/80x80" width="80" /></a></div>
  							<div class="details">
  								<h3 class="who"><a href="/groups/140">Sarah Kennedy</a></h3>
  								<p class="what">In this dedication of their own physical condition, but for basic human rights. The passion for us together offer an ever-richer life and property,</p>
  							</div>
  						</div>
						
  					</div> 
  					<div id="following" class="tabs-panel" style="display: none"> 
  						<h1>ARE WE RENDERING ALL THE 'WATCHED' THINGS HERE? (QUESTIONS, PEOPLE, GROUPS, ETC.)</h1>
  					</div> 
  					<div id="messages" class="tabs-panel" style="display: none"> 
